John Qualen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Qualen 0 John Qualen (born Johan Mandt Kvalen, December 8, 1899 – September 12, 1987) was a Canadian-American character actor of Norwegian heritage who specialized in Scandinavian roles.
